</p>
<p>In a minute, we'll register this as a service.</p>
<p>Down below, add <code>$encoded = $this-&gt;passwordEncoder-&gt;encodePassword()</code> and pass it
the User - which is <code>$entity</code> - and the plain-text password: <code>$entity-&gt;getPlainPassword()</code>.
Finish it with <code>$entity-&gt;setPassword($encoded)</code>:</p>
