<h2 id="registering-the-subscriber-as-a-service">Registering the Subscriber as a Service <a class="headerlink" href="encoding-user-password#registering-the-subscriber-as-a-service" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Ok, the event subscriber is perfect! To hook it up - you guessed it - we'll register
it as a service. Open <code>app/config/services.yml</code> and add a new service called
<code>app.doctrine.hash_password_listener</code>. Set the class. And you guys know by now that
I love to autowire things. It doesn't always work, but it's great when it does:</p>
